snippet.title: PAPERHEAD DEMO TRAILER
snippet.description:
PAPERHEAD is a mix of a fast-paced movement boomer shooter and an adventure horror game, featuring a unique soundtrack.

In the cute cardboard world, something horrible happened...
Uncover the dark truth and find out...
...WHY WOULD CARDBOARD...BLEED?

WISHLIST ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2680280/PAPERHEAD/
====
DOWNLOAD THE DEMO: https://paperhead.itch.io/paperhead-demo
FOLLOW THE TWITTER: https://twitter.com/PAPERHEAD_GAME
JOIN THE DISCORD SERVER: https://discord.gg/ddGyJyRStq
